Since im youg im an interressed by the news, i was often in front of my television for looking the World News on TF1 or others channel .I was thinking that this work is a important and funny job. I also found that the journalism work is interessing, ask some questions to people and record their respond was funny. So, when I was 14 years old, i do a stage in 3rd class, I view a community manager at work, what are they working days were organised, what he do and what he dont do. I found that it was very interessing and well paid so I demand to this person wich studies he as do for work as community manager. He respond me that, in the past, he was doing studies in communication. So I search what type of studies i can do for exercing this job, I found the license Information-communication. When i was in "terminale", I wrote on Parcoursup some school that do this studie, I demand Rennes 2 because it's not to far away from my house. for all of this reasons I choose this studie.
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In others words, when focused on the textbox below, the page will record each time you hit a key or select text with your mouse. All of the data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file. More information about the motivation of this project and the format of the producted data are available here.
